{"tid":1419634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對山王比賽，櫻木花道對安山教練說：「 我只有現在啊! 」","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T21:24:19.000Z","uid":282836,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"64e4a53b886e47f233f9c1d8b5dc7430101a2493","tid":1419634,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:06:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/61UdomA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F61UdomA.jpg&h=f067bcab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">安西（和理非）</span>無辦法阻止<span style=\"color: gold;\">櫻木（勇武）</span>再上場對抗<span style=\"color: red;\">山王（黑政權）</span>，即使<span style=\"color: gold;\">安西教練</span>知道<span style=\"color: gold;\">櫻木</span>有可能賠上運動員的生命，但已無能力阻止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">安西教練</span>說： 「<span style=\"color: gold;\">櫻木</span>，既然你堅持上戰場抗爭，可否答應我減少<ins>受傷</ins>和<ins>保留多些HP</ins>，才有力量戰勝<span style=\"color: red;\">山王</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n利申： 安西教練<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不分化，不割蓆，不受傷，不被捕，不殺人<br />\n「唇亡齒寒」<br />\n Be Water, My Friend</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"23fdb72d2e0dc5c61eb7ae25cd1c7ca452045122","tid":1419634,"uid":282836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:15:56.000Z","msg":"從6月9日起到8月4日，經歷 14次大型集會或遊行，最後都發生衝突，被捕義士共420人，平均每次被手捕30人。如果到十月一日，還有17次有機會發生衝突，到那天將近一千被捕。希望勇武手足冷靜想想如何減低被捕和受傷才是關鍵。仇恨只會換來更大的仇恨，我們不是黑政權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5j5ezV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5j5ezV.jpg&h=4daf8d07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28433abb610482e7d9e875f4b7d61a9b7827be5a","tid":1419634,"uid":293443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:18:11.000Z","msg":"每次看這幕我都好感動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f44dd51a22c6aaddfe5c489a310a946335f3bf","tid":1419634,"uid":264254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0